314
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:45,830
Mne?

315
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:49,750
Mizerný starec!

316
00:18:30,490 --> 00:18:31,910
Sú krásne.

317
00:18:34,460 --> 00:18:35,940
To je darček.

318
00:18:35,940 --> 00:18:36,690
Jin Se Ryeong?

319
00:18:36,690 --> 00:18:38,110
Samozrejme!

320
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:40,450
Kto iný by ti priniesol kyticu za prehru,

321
00:18:40,450 --> 00:18:42,870
