335
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:38,950
Jin Se Ryeong.

336
00:19:38,950 --> 00:19:40,400
Ty...

337
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:46,000
Ako medzinárodná hviezda, Jin Se Ryeong,
